WEBVTT

00:01:14.250 --> 00:01:17.874
Is it ready?

00:01:17.875 --> 00:01:19.624
When did I ask for it?

00:01:19.625 --> 00:01:20.874
Almost done.

00:01:20.875 --> 00:01:22.874
Come back.

00:01:22.875 --> 00:01:24.624
Get back here right now.

00:01:24.625 --> 00:01:26.999
I'll slog all day
and you'll have fun.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.333
What is it?

00:01:31.042 --> 00:01:34.832
I asked for some chips.
Why can't you get it?

00:01:34.833 --> 00:01:39.374
Why can't you answer?

00:01:39.375 --> 00:01:44.249
You slut! I'll bring home the money
and you'll enjoy it.

00:01:44.250 --> 00:01:48.457
Are you tired of me?

00:01:48.458 --> 00:01:51.291
Say it... Say it...

00:01:51.292 --> 00:01:53.125
Let Mom go.

00:01:54.167 --> 00:01:56.000
Dad, let go of Mom.

00:01:56.250 --> 00:01:59.541
Bloody hell! All I wanted was some chips.

00:01:59.542 --> 00:02:01.750
Leave Mom alone.

00:02:02.458 --> 00:02:04.624
I'm beating my wife.
What's your problem?

00:02:04.625 --> 00:02:06.417
Go study.

00:02:06.583 --> 00:02:10.916
I've been trying to concentrate
for a long time but I can't.

00:02:10.917 --> 00:02:12.457
This has been happening
for a long time.

00:02:12.458 --> 00:02:15.332
- Please stop. Will you stop now, please?
- Get out.

00:02:15.333 --> 00:02:17.999
Go to your room.
Nothing is going on here.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.541
Your dad will cool down in some time.

00:02:20.542 --> 00:02:23.832
- Then the three of us...
- Will go out for dinner.

00:02:23.833 --> 00:02:26.416
It's your birthday at midnight.

00:02:26.417 --> 00:02:30.958
Listen to your mother for once.
Go to your room.

00:02:31.458 --> 00:02:38.707
Finish your homework.
I'll finish... Anyway...

00:02:38.708 --> 00:02:42.166
Did you give birth to this thing?
This bastard?

00:02:42.167 --> 00:02:44.249
He can't be mine.

00:02:44.250 --> 00:02:47.249
He's so disobedient.

00:02:47.250 --> 00:02:48.374
He can't be my son.

00:02:48.375 --> 00:02:52.541
- Who else did you sleep with?
- Let Mom go.

00:02:52.542 --> 00:02:55.125
Let Mom go, you rascal!

00:03:07.417 --> 00:03:10.000
Did you not hear me, idiot?
Let Mom go.

00:03:16.958 --> 00:03:18.249
Say it again.

00:03:18.250 --> 00:03:20.750
Let Mom go, rascal.

00:03:23.458 --> 00:03:25.542
- Say it again.
- Let Mom go, rascal.

00:03:29.125 --> 00:03:32.792
- Say it again.
- Let Mom go, rascal.

00:03:33.208 --> 00:03:36.583
- Say it again.
- Let Mom go, rascal.

00:03:42.208 --> 00:03:44.958
I'll beat you to a pulp.

00:03:45.625 --> 00:03:48.458
Get lost.

00:03:48.625 --> 00:03:51.582
Don't forget that I'm the one who pays
for stuff around here.

00:03:51.583 --> 00:03:55.082
You've taught him to misbehave like this.

00:03:55.083 --> 00:04:00.541
Who else did you sleep with?
Is he my son? Tell me.

00:04:00.542 --> 00:04:02.832
I'll kill you.

00:04:02.833 --> 00:04:05.082
Answer me.

00:04:05.083 --> 00:04:09.375
Or I'll thrash answers out of you.

00:04:44.792 --> 00:04:47.958
Hello, Bhowanipore Police Station?

00:04:48.792 --> 00:04:51.958
There has been a murder.

00:04:53.167 --> 00:04:56.499
I've murdered my father
just moments back.

00:04:56.500 --> 00:05:01.332
The address is
105, Harish Mukherjee Road.

00:05:01.333 --> 00:05:05.958
Once you cross the park,
it's the third house on the right.

00:05:06.708 --> 00:05:12.208
Yes... Please come fast.
Okay.

00:06:01.625 --> 00:06:03.833
Happy birthday to me.

00:06:09.708 --> 00:06:13.707
<i>This is my father,
Debiprasad Bhowmik.</i>

00:06:13.708 --> 00:06:17.458
<i>And this little boy is me.</i>

00:06:17.750 --> 00:06:19.541
<i>I'll give you a brief introduction.</i>

00:06:19.542 --> 00:06:21.916
<i>Then I'll be able to tell you
the actual story properly.</i>

00:06:21.917 --> 00:06:25.749
<i>Otherwise, we'll spend
all our time... Anyway.</i>

00:06:25.750 --> 00:06:29.624
<i>My father was a serious makeup artist.</i>

00:06:29.625 --> 00:06:31.957
<i>It was a form of worship for him.</i>

00:06:31.958 --> 00:06:34.249
<i>He didn't care about anyone.</i>

00:06:34.250 --> 00:06:40.042
<i>Once he scolded an actor for chatting
in the middle of the makeup session.</i>

00:06:40.417 --> 00:06:43.792
<i>After that everyone fell in line.</i>

00:06:44.458 --> 00:06:45.917
<i>Anyway...</i>

00:06:46.167 --> 00:06:48.542
<i>My mother left us when I was very young.</i>

00:06:48.583 --> 00:06:50.333
<i>My father meant the world to me.</i>

00:06:50.625 --> 00:06:53.999
<i>I followed in his footstep
and started a career in makeup.</i>

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.542
<i>I started studying it.</i>

00:06:56.708 --> 00:06:58.332
<i>Father taught me as well.</i>

00:06:58.333 --> 00:07:00.250
<i>I started learning with all my heart.</i>

00:07:00.292 --> 00:07:04.957
<i>I started going to the
neighbourhood library.</i>

00:07:04.958 --> 00:07:09.250
<i>I began devouring all the books on makeup
I could get my hands on.</i>

00:07:11.375 --> 00:07:14.833
<i>Then with the access to the internet,
I was unstoppable.</i>

00:07:14.875 --> 00:07:19.166
<i>Not just makeup, I started delving into
prosthetics, special effects...</i>

00:07:19.167 --> 00:07:25.291
<i>plastic surgery, colours, drawing, art etc.</i>

00:07:25.292 --> 00:07:28.082
<i>National and international artistes...
Oh, yeah...</i>

00:07:28.083 --> 00:07:31.000
<i>I completely forgot to tell you...
That's where I got my name...</i>

00:07:31.167 --> 00:07:35.332
Van Gogh is the real deal, bro.
He is a true artiste.

00:07:35.333 --> 00:07:38.207
He was never appreciated
during his life.

00:07:38.208 --> 00:07:39.624
He never sold a painting in his lifetime.

00:07:39.625 --> 00:07:43.332
But now the entire world
is crazy about his work.

00:07:43.333 --> 00:07:46.249
Actually, he was much ahead
of his time.

00:07:46.250 --> 00:07:47.250
Genius!

00:07:47.251 --> 00:07:49.541
- He had enough support.
- What do you mean?

00:07:49.542 --> 00:07:54.332
He was nothing without the support
of his brother Theo and friend Ganguin.

00:07:54.333 --> 00:07:56.499
- What are you saying?
- Basically, he was mad.

00:07:56.500 --> 00:07:58.768
Just because he cut off his ear
doesn't make him a genius.

00:07:58.792 --> 00:08:03.958
You can call Picasso or Dali genius.

00:08:04.083 --> 00:08:06.749
- They brought in a newness in their art.
- That Van Gogh did too.

00:08:06.750 --> 00:08:09.124
Please, no point saying that, buddy.

00:08:09.125 --> 00:08:12.457
You can say Van Gogh's strokes
had newness in them.

00:08:12.458 --> 00:08:14.374
Otherwise, it's all Monet and Manet.

00:08:14.375 --> 00:08:15.791
They're all amateurs.

00:08:15.792 --> 00:08:18.417
- What?
- Excuse me.

00:08:19.625 --> 00:08:24.167
Everyone is an amateur
compared to Leonardo.

00:08:24.417 --> 00:08:27.375
The names you just mentioned
were just painters.

00:08:27.500 --> 00:08:31.624
But if there is true genius
then it has to be Leonardo da Vinci.

00:08:31.625 --> 00:08:34.208
He wasn't only an artiste
but a scientist too.

00:08:34.250 --> 00:08:39.957
According to you, Van Gogh, Picasso,
Rembrandt, Dali are all amateurs.

00:08:39.958 --> 00:08:41.582
- Absolutely!
- Are you kidding me?

00:08:41.583 --> 00:08:42.916
Why would I?

00:08:42.917 --> 00:08:45.082
If you want to argue,
you must study about it.

00:08:45.083 --> 00:08:51.749
The only artiste who might come close
is probably Michelangelo.

00:08:51.750 --> 00:08:52.874
But Leo is Leo.

00:08:52.875 --> 00:08:56.375
- Have you been smoking up?
- Tell us how?

00:08:56.500 --> 00:08:57.958
- How?
- Yes.

00:08:58.125 --> 00:08:59.957
I'll explain it to you.

00:08:59.958 --> 00:09:02.582
One must do some research
into the subject.

00:09:02.583 --> 00:09:03.542
Watch your mouth.

00:09:03.543 --> 00:09:10.250
Da Vinci was the first to prove to the world
that art is science and science is art.

00:09:10.667 --> 00:09:12.457
Forget the paintings.

00:09:12.458 --> 00:09:16.791
The sculptures, the designs for helicopters
and other machines...

00:09:16.792 --> 00:09:21.874
Blueprints of different weapons, the hydraulics,
the pulley and so many other works.

00:09:21.875 --> 00:09:25.791
Tell me who else has been able to do it.

00:09:25.792 --> 00:09:28.957
Has anyone come close to his achievements?

00:09:28.958 --> 00:09:29.958
Give me one name.

00:09:31.417 --> 00:09:35.333
He is a Da Vinci fanboy.

00:09:36.833 --> 00:09:41.708
So what's your name?
Da Vinci's fan, Vinci Da?

00:09:45.542 --> 00:09:47.333
<i>Whatever my name was...</i>

00:09:47.542 --> 00:09:53.667
<i>but the name given by those two
intellectuals that day became popular.</i>

00:09:53.750 --> 00:09:55.208
<i>That name stuck with me.</i>

00:09:55.375 --> 00:09:58.250
<i>Yes, I'm Vinci Da.</i>

00:09:58.625 --> 00:10:00.208
<i>And this is my story.</i>

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:04.957
I am happy to announce
that the honourable court...

00:10:04.958 --> 00:10:08.833
has been pleased to rule in favour of
my client Mr. Shyamsundar Jaiswal.

00:10:08.958 --> 00:10:13.457
He has been awarded unconditional acquittal
with all damages included.

00:10:13.458 --> 00:10:16.332
Due to lack of any substantial evidence
against him.

00:10:16.333 --> 00:10:18.792
Mr. Jaiswal, your reaction on your release?

00:10:19.083 --> 00:10:21.291
I am very happy.

00:10:21.292 --> 00:10:23.582
I've been acquitted.
I knew I was innocent.

00:10:23.583 --> 00:10:25.059
And the court said the same thing today.

00:10:25.083 --> 00:10:28.374
So, are you saying the Rs. 2500 crore scam
didn't happen?

00:10:28.375 --> 00:10:30.458
Please don't harass my client. Enough.

00:10:30.583 --> 00:10:32.542
- No more questions.
- Let me take this.

00:10:32.750 --> 00:10:34.707
See, the scam did happen.

00:10:34.708 --> 00:10:36.207
And someone has done it.

00:10:36.208 --> 00:10:39.958
But High Court just said
that that person is not me.

00:10:40.125 --> 00:10:42.082
Mr. Jaiswal, one last question.

00:10:42.083 --> 00:10:44.624
The company, the hotel,
the resort is all yours.

00:10:44.625 --> 00:10:45.832
Then, who did the scam?

00:10:45.833 --> 00:10:50.583
Just blame it
on the legendary criminal Nando Ghosh.

00:10:54.042 --> 00:10:56.875
Hail Lord Vishnu!

00:10:57.083 --> 00:10:59.917
Hail Lord Vishnu!

00:11:00.042 --> 00:11:04.750
Put this on his head, heart and feet.

00:11:05.125 --> 00:11:07.957
<i>The person whose shadow
I've been under...</i>

00:11:07.958 --> 00:11:10.250
<i>The person I learnt my craft from...</i>

00:11:10.417 --> 00:11:13.708
<i>The person who never let me feel
the absence of a mother...</i>

00:11:13.833 --> 00:11:16.292
<i>That person left me alone one day.</i>

00:11:16.625 --> 00:11:20.000
<i>I wanted to remember
his living, smiling face.</i>

00:11:20.375 --> 00:11:23.042
<i>Not the stone cold dead face.</i>

00:11:23.167 --> 00:11:26.958
<i>I avoided looking at his face
while performing the last rites.</i>

00:11:27.208 --> 00:11:30.042
<i>But finally when I saw his face...</i>

00:11:30.458 --> 00:11:33.917
<i>I couldn't bear looking at it.</i>

00:11:46.250 --> 00:11:50.125
Sir, where are you going?

00:11:50.917 --> 00:11:53.958
- He's gone crazy.
- He just lost his dad.

00:11:57.125 --> 00:11:59.625
He used to love his father a lot.

00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:10.583
What are you doing?

00:12:10.875 --> 00:12:13.333
Have you lost your mind?

00:12:13.625 --> 00:12:16.458
Can't you see his face
is looking so lifeless?

00:12:17.250 --> 00:12:19.625
My father was an artiste.

00:12:19.917 --> 00:12:22.791
He should look good for his farewell.

00:12:22.792 --> 00:12:24.833
Just these flowers won't do justice.

00:12:26.208 --> 00:12:27.666
What is he talking about?

00:12:27.667 --> 00:12:29.792
He's gone bonkers.

00:12:36.708 --> 00:12:38.583
<i>Makeup was done.</i>

00:12:38.875 --> 00:12:40.958
<i>My father entered the set.</i>

00:12:41.292 --> 00:12:45.208
<i>And we waited quietly
for the shot to be over.</i>

00:12:46.542 --> 00:12:50.125
<i>I met one of Father's friends
from the film industry.</i>

00:12:50.167 --> 00:12:53.375
<i>He said time for experimenting
and studying is over.</i>

00:12:53.458 --> 00:12:55.832
<i>I must earn a living now.</i>

00:12:55.833 --> 00:12:59.917
<i>I'll never be famous
if I don't get my act together.</i>

00:13:00.167 --> 00:13:03.708
<i>He gave me the contact
of a famous director.</i>

00:13:03.875 --> 00:13:06.292
<i>He asked me to meet for work.</i>

00:13:11.667 --> 00:13:16.125
<i>I forgot to tell you about Jaya.</i>

00:13:16.208 --> 00:13:18.667
<i>She is very sweet girl
from my neighbourhood.</i>

00:13:18.750 --> 00:13:24.208
<i>I used to like her a lot.</i>

00:13:24.542 --> 00:13:28.208
<i>I was very serious about her, I swear.</i>

00:13:28.417 --> 00:13:30.375
<i>You can call it love.</i>

00:13:30.458 --> 00:13:33.666
<i>She was by my side through the ups
and downs, even from a distance.</i>

00:13:33.667 --> 00:13:37.167
<i>She was my inspiration
to do great work.</i>

00:13:37.542 --> 00:13:40.625
<i>It was my plan to do something great
for her.</i>

00:13:41.250 --> 00:13:44.375
<i>But it was difficult to meet her
or talk to her.</i>

00:13:44.458 --> 00:13:46.041
<i>Her father was very strict.</i>

00:13:46.042 --> 00:13:47.999
And what did you do after that?

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:50.458
I drove the car back, sir.

00:13:50.708 --> 00:13:54.624
But the accused left the hotel lobby
with his girlfriend, Ms. Gupta.

00:13:54.625 --> 00:13:56.249
Where did you join them?

00:13:56.250 --> 00:13:58.332
Boss had called me.

00:13:58.333 --> 00:14:00.291
So, I met them on the way.

00:14:00.292 --> 00:14:02.541
And I took the keys.

00:14:02.542 --> 00:14:05.667
So, were you driving the car
when the accident happened?

00:14:09.167 --> 00:14:10.499
Yes, sir.

00:14:10.500 --> 00:14:16.458
And your boss's girlfriend
was sitting with you instead of him?

00:14:16.667 --> 00:14:17.625
Yes, sir.

00:14:17.626 --> 00:14:19.042
Sure?

00:14:20.292 --> 00:14:21.457
Yes, sir.

00:14:21.458 --> 00:14:24.416
So, when the car hit the divider,
killing Ms. Gupta on the spot...

00:14:24.417 --> 00:14:26.917
you were driving the car,
not your boss?

00:14:28.833 --> 00:14:30.375
Yes, sir.

00:14:31.292 --> 00:14:35.416
And before the crash, the car ran over
five people sleeping on the pavement...

00:14:35.417 --> 00:14:37.374
you were driving the car,
not your boss?

00:14:37.375 --> 00:14:42.917
They constantly want fresh blood.
Is this a blood bank?

00:14:42.958 --> 00:14:44.542
Sir, Debiprasad's son is here.

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:47.332
Send him here.

00:14:47.333 --> 00:14:49.416
- Here he comes.
- Who?

00:14:49.417 --> 00:14:50.333
Come here.

00:14:50.334 --> 00:14:53.208
Are you talking about Debi Bhowmik?

00:14:53.500 --> 00:14:55.207
Isn't he from the Ice Ages?

00:14:55.208 --> 00:14:57.417
He passed away recently.

00:14:57.667 --> 00:15:03.083
A common friend asked me to meet his son
to give him work.

00:15:04.750 --> 00:15:05.667
Hello, sir.

00:15:05.668 --> 00:15:09.375
Abhijeet told me about you.

00:15:09.583 --> 00:15:14.042
Do you have any skills or are you
using your father's name to get work?

00:15:14.708 --> 00:15:16.083
I am good at what I do.

00:15:17.042 --> 00:15:18.250
Great.

00:15:19.750 --> 00:15:22.582
Why did you leave Sujit's shoot?

00:15:22.583 --> 00:15:23.875
What?

00:15:24.625 --> 00:15:26.583
I felt insulted that's why.

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:28.042
Why?

00:15:28.333 --> 00:15:35.125
He told me before the shoot started
that we have to compete with Bombay.

00:15:35.250 --> 00:15:37.207
I was doing the prosthetic makeup.

00:15:37.208 --> 00:15:40.500
A man who had been in a blast.

00:15:40.625 --> 00:15:44.125
I had spent four and a half hours
to get the actor ready.

00:15:44.417 --> 00:15:47.708
Sujit said it was excellent work.

00:15:48.167 --> 00:15:50.125
But then he said...

00:15:50.458 --> 00:15:54.875
The prosthetic makeup was so realistic,
the blood, the skin...

00:15:55.583 --> 00:15:59.042
that the Censor Board
would chop that scene off.

00:15:59.375 --> 00:16:03.749
If that was the case,
why did he push me so hard?

00:16:03.750 --> 00:16:05.542
That's why I quit.

00:16:05.833 --> 00:16:09.167
You want to surpass
the Bombay film industry, right?

00:16:09.583 --> 00:16:11.167
I don't want to.
I can.

00:16:11.625 --> 00:16:15.582
And I can do it in half the budget.

00:16:15.583 --> 00:16:17.667
Got it.

00:16:18.208 --> 00:16:20.250
Hey, come here.

00:16:20.542 --> 00:16:25.666
Call Vikram and push the call time
by an hour.

00:16:25.667 --> 00:16:26.250
Okay.

00:16:26.251 --> 00:16:29.124
Take him to the actress
and explain the character to him.

00:16:29.125 --> 00:16:29.542
Okay.

00:16:29.543 --> 00:16:30.833
Go with him.

00:16:31.250 --> 00:16:33.582
- Go ahead.
- Thank you, sir.

00:16:33.583 --> 00:16:36.458
I want to see your work.

00:16:38.083 --> 00:16:39.583
Fresh blood.

00:16:41.708 --> 00:16:44.582
- You are unneccesarily tensed.
- It's not about that.

00:16:44.583 --> 00:16:47.249
- It's nothing. Nothing will happen.
- Things are getting worse.

00:16:47.250 --> 00:16:50.457
It's not about confidence. It's okay.
Nothing to worry about.

00:16:50.458 --> 00:16:52.082
These people again.

00:16:52.083 --> 00:16:54.374
No comments. No comments.

00:16:54.375 --> 00:16:56.666
You'll get to know anyway.
Please move out of the way.

00:16:56.667 --> 00:16:58.541
- Please give way.
- Excuse me. Excuse us.

00:16:58.542 --> 00:17:00.958
Please... No comments...

00:17:05.625 --> 00:17:07.417
He got the acquittal after all.

00:17:07.625 --> 00:17:09.166
He was supposed to get it anyway.

00:17:09.167 --> 00:17:10.707
The last judge got transferred.

00:17:10.708 --> 00:17:13.083
The one before him died mysteriously.

00:17:13.542 --> 00:17:15.583
Who will take this kind of pressure?

00:17:16.125 --> 00:17:17.458
What happened to the girl?

00:17:17.542 --> 00:17:18.582
What else?

00:17:18.583 --> 00:17:20.624
If she has money, she'll appeal again.

00:17:20.625 --> 00:17:21.916
Next, it'll go to the Supreme Court.

00:17:21.917 --> 00:17:25.374
The person who was raped will have to
prove that she was raped yet again.

00:17:25.375 --> 00:17:26.917
Ridiculous!

00:17:27.042 --> 00:17:29.082
He is very perverted.

00:17:29.083 --> 00:17:30.957
He has a distorted mind.

00:17:30.958 --> 00:17:32.917
He is very experimental.

00:17:33.208 --> 00:17:34.792
And he films himself in the act.

00:17:35.250 --> 00:17:36.417
Hey!

00:17:37.042 --> 00:17:38.332
What have you done?

00:17:38.333 --> 00:17:40.583
Didn't my assistant brief you?

