before I leave.

00:19:18.333 --> 00:19:24.166
It's just your luck that even after being
such a bad actor, you're still a super star.

00:19:24.167 --> 00:19:25.499
And you know that very well.

00:19:25.500 --> 00:19:27.750
So don't show your expertise
about makeup.

00:19:27.875 --> 00:19:29.541
Makeup is an art.

00:19:29.542 --> 00:19:31.500
Your thick brain can't handle it.

00:19:31.750 --> 00:19:33.542
Bloody swine!

00:19:55.292 --> 00:19:56.542
You didn't get the job?

00:19:57.375 --> 00:19:58.542
Nope.

00:20:00.208 --> 00:20:02.583
They abused me and threw me out,
bloody idiots.

00:20:05.625 --> 00:20:07.000
Forget about them.

00:20:08.583 --> 00:20:10.875
You'll find another job.

00:20:10.917 --> 00:20:12.042
Like hell, I will.

00:20:13.333 --> 00:20:15.167
They're very powerful people.

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:18.583
They'll not let me work
in the film industry anymore.

00:20:21.542 --> 00:20:22.833
That's okay.

00:20:23.542 --> 00:20:26.083
You can... find some other work...

