What will you say?

00:21:29.292 --> 00:21:30.542
You know...

00:21:32.375 --> 00:21:35.542
"May my heart be yours.

00:21:37.333 --> 00:21:42.208
- May your heart...
- May your heart...

00:21:49.917 --> 00:21:51.542
Catch that man!
Pickpocket!

