<i>But strangely, his mother got scared.</i>

00:23:50.000 --> 00:23:52.583
<i>She thought he was crazy
and left him alone.</i>

00:23:52.958 --> 00:23:55.499
<i>He killed his father.
His mother left him.</i>

00:23:55.500 --> 00:23:58.916
<i>For the lack of opportunity,
situation, time and money...</i>

00:23:58.917 --> 00:24:00.958
<i>He couldn't become a criminal lawyer.</i>

00:24:01.250 --> 00:24:04.750
<i>Instead, he got a criminal record.</i>

00:24:05.208 --> 00:24:09.083
<i>But he was not one to give up.</i>

00:24:09.250 --> 00:24:13.542
<i>He continued studying Law
even inside the asylum.</i>

00:24:14.750 --> 00:24:19.583
<i>He would feel very unsettled
if he was not close to the Law.</i>

00:24:20.500 --> 00:24:24.417
<i>So, he started going to the court
after being released from the asylum.</i>

00:24:24.542 --> 00:24:27.458
<i>He started taking notes
on the difficult cases.</i>

00:24:27.917 --> 00:24:31.167
<i>Then he set up his own office
outside the courtroom.</i>

00:24:31.958 --> 00:24:35.792
<i>Experienced lawyers would drop by
to take his advice on cases.</i>

00:24:36.250 --> 00:24:38.041
<i>He earned a lot of money.</i>

00:24:38.042 --> 00:24:43.542
<i>But by that time, Adi Bose
had completely lost his mind.</i>

00:24:45.833 --> 00:24:51.250
Mukherjee, of all the police stations
under me...

00:24:52.458 --> 00:24:54.750
yours is the most efficient.

00:24:55.375 --> 00:24:56.893
So, see to it,
this doesn't happen again.

00:24:56.917 --> 00:24:58.000
It won't, sir.

