If we get a high profile case.

00:25:00.125 --> 00:25:01.958
Involving ministers, businessmen etc...

00:25:02.042 --> 00:25:04.268
- Then we'll need your help.
- Of course, I'll look into it.

00:25:04.292 --> 00:25:06.374
- You can't go in.
- It's urgent.

00:25:06.375 --> 00:25:08.124
Sorry, sir.
He just barged in.

00:25:08.125 --> 00:25:10.458
Wait. Yes, tell me.

00:25:10.833 --> 00:25:13.042
There's a pickpocket in my car.

00:25:13.583 --> 00:25:15.625
He was beaten very badly by a mob.
He's dying.

00:25:16.500 --> 00:25:17.750
Please look into it.

00:25:19.583 --> 00:25:21.000
Take a look.
Give him the keys.

00:25:21.167 --> 00:25:22.500
The car is not locked.

00:25:24.875 --> 00:25:25.916
Where did you find him?

00:25:25.917 --> 00:25:27.292
I was on my way to the court.

00:25:27.417 --> 00:25:29.292
Saw him... Brought him here.

00:25:29.625 --> 00:25:30.917
I'm a lawyer, sir.

00:25:32.750 --> 00:25:34.792
Where do you practice?
Alipore Court?

00:25:34.833 --> 00:25:36.666
No... Actually, I don't...

00:25:36.667 --> 00:25:38.875
I haven't started yet.
About to start my practice.

