What if he died?

00:25:56.542 --> 00:25:57.708
But, sir, the Law?

00:25:57.750 --> 00:25:59.071
Law comes before everything else.

00:25:59.208 --> 00:26:01.333
Life and death are secondary.

00:26:01.500 --> 00:26:02.500
Okay.

