There are no provisions for pickpocketing
in the Indian Penal Code.

00:26:41.333 --> 00:26:42.601
You'll have to book him under theft.

00:26:42.625 --> 00:26:44.291
378 and 379.

00:26:44.292 --> 00:26:46.476
And there's mental trauma caused
to the person he stole from.

00:26:46.500 --> 00:26:49.940
That amounts to voluntary harassment, so you
can charge him under Section 323, as well.

00:26:51.542 --> 00:26:52.625
Good bye.

00:26:57.083 --> 00:26:58.083
What was his name?

00:27:37.375 --> 00:27:39.458
Are you done?

00:27:40.667 --> 00:27:45.791
How much longer?

00:27:45.792 --> 00:27:49.500
You have to wait.
You're too restless.

00:27:49.708 --> 00:27:53.750
Sit quietly. Don't move.
And don't blink at all.

00:27:56.625 --> 00:27:59.167
Irritating me all the time.

