Hey, what's the matter with you?

00:28:28.292 --> 00:28:32.250
- Do you want some tea, Uncle?
- Yeah.

00:28:34.625 --> 00:28:36.124
I left town for a few days...

00:28:36.125 --> 00:28:38.750
and you've screwed things up
in the meantime.

00:28:39.250 --> 00:28:41.667
Got it.

00:28:43.000 --> 00:28:47.291
What have I done wrong this time?

