<i>He hears the dead scream</i>

00:32:39.875 --> 00:32:41.457
Does Mr. Vinci live here?

00:32:41.458 --> 00:32:43.249
Da... It's Vinci Da.

00:32:43.250 --> 00:32:44.250
Tell me.

00:32:45.250 --> 00:32:47.208
I wanted to talk to you about a film.

00:32:48.125 --> 00:32:49.832
Film...

00:32:49.833 --> 00:32:51.958
Please take a seat.
Please sit.

00:32:52.250 --> 00:32:55.292
Give me a minute.

00:32:57.208 --> 00:32:59.500
Sorry... The house is a mess...

00:33:01.750 --> 00:33:04.583
- Would you like some tea?
- No, thank you.

00:33:05.708 --> 00:33:08.083
- There's a film being made.
- Oh, okay.

00:33:09.625 --> 00:33:12.333
Shyamsundar Jaiswal, the businessman.

00:33:13.542 --> 00:33:17.125
- Shyamsundar was in...
- Jail but not anymore.

