00:34:27.750 --> 00:34:29.832
The person whose face we'll be copying...

00:34:29.833 --> 00:34:34.542
the colour of his skin,
each wrinkle...

00:34:34.625 --> 00:34:35.791
the colour of his eyes...

00:34:35.792 --> 00:34:36.708
- Will it match?
- Absolutely...

00:34:36.709 --> 00:34:38.792
