00:34:40.708 --> 00:34:45.541
For a perfect fit,
I'll have to measure Bumba's face.

00:34:45.542 --> 00:34:48.999
The mask has to be fixed
on his face.

00:34:49.000 --> 00:34:50.934
- You get it?
- You'll have to make a sample first.

00:34:50.958 --> 00:34:53.500
Make one according to my face.

00:34:53.875 --> 00:34:54.875
Let me show it to them.

00:34:55.042 --> 00:34:56.708
Let them see it.

