If it's approved you can go
and take Bumba's measurement.

00:35:01.500 --> 00:35:03.332
We're in a hurry.

00:35:03.333 --> 00:35:05.167
It'll be done on time.

00:35:05.500 --> 00:35:10.417
I'll have to buy the chemicals
and materials.

00:35:10.625 --> 00:35:14.000
- So, if you can give some advance...
- Of course... Here you go.

00:35:14.375 --> 00:35:14.792
What's this?

00:35:14.793 --> 00:35:20.250
