the daughter's attempted suicide...

00:52:04.833 --> 00:52:08.542
These were absolutely unplanned surprises.

00:52:11.250 --> 00:52:13.292
But Shyamsundar is in jail.

00:52:13.708 --> 00:52:17.625
He's been destroying so many lives...

00:52:18.167 --> 00:52:20.167
Now, he can't anymore.

00:52:20.708 --> 00:52:21.708
Clear?

00:52:24.917 --> 00:52:26.250
Got it.

00:52:26.958 --> 00:52:28.958
But I don't know.

00:52:29.250 --> 00:52:31.708
I'm just an ordinary artiste.

00:52:32.083 --> 00:52:36.250
- I don't want to play God...
- You don't need to be God to punish Evil.

00:52:37.667 --> 00:52:39.458
You need Ubermenschen.

00:52:41.583 --> 00:52:44.542
When God is dead,
they fix things.

00:52:44.583 --> 00:52:47.083
What's right, what's wrong?

00:52:47.250 --> 00:52:49.958
What's just, what's unjust?

00:52:51.167 --> 00:52:53.458
Have you heard of Nietzsche?

00:52:54.250 --> 00:52:56.083
Is he an international lawyer?

00:52:56.292 --> 00:52:58.000
Neither a lawyer nor an artiste.

00:52:58.500 --> 00:52:59.875
A philosopher.

00:53:00.500 --> 00:53:04.208
He came up with the term "Ubermensch".

00:53:04.375 --> 00:53:12.375
It means a powerful, talented,
sharp Superman...

00:53:14.083 --> 00:53:16.792
Man-made laws, rules, society...

00:53:17.917 --> 00:53:19.833
He's above it all.

00:53:20.083 --> 00:53:23.167
He decides he wants to commit a crime.

00:53:25.083 --> 00:53:26.332
No one will be able to catch him.

00:53:26.333 --> 00:53:27.458
He's so sharp.

00:53:29.583 --> 00:53:30.917
Just like me.

00:53:34.875 --> 00:53:38.000
You can do it too.

00:53:39.458 --> 00:53:44.666
But you'll have to perform your duties as a
talented artiste and a responsible citizen.

00:53:44.667 --> 00:53:46.042
Let's see who's next?

00:53:47.542 --> 00:53:49.917
<i>Manas Saha, minister's son.</i>

00:53:50.250 --> 00:53:52.167
<i>He's killed people while driving drunk.</i>

00:53:52.333 --> 00:53:53.833
Who's going to match it?

00:53:54.458 --> 00:53:56.375
The artiste will match it.

00:53:57.375 --> 00:54:00.000
This is going to be Vinci Da's "Mona Lisa".

00:54:02.250 --> 00:54:03.250
Ready?

00:54:26.125 --> 00:54:28.083
<i>But I'm an artiste.</i>

00:54:28.125 --> 00:54:31.207
<i>If my work benefits someone, great.</i>

00:54:31.208 --> 00:54:33.250
<i>But why should it harm someone?</i>

00:54:39.500 --> 00:54:42.083
The Nobel Prize for peace...

00:54:43.625 --> 00:54:47.458
Do you know where Alfred Nobel
got that money from?

00:54:48.583 --> 00:54:53.250
By selling dynamite. Bombs. Explosive.

00:54:54.875 --> 00:54:57.125
What does that have to do with the artiste?

00:54:57.500 --> 00:55:00.292
Let's start with your idol.

00:55:01.750 --> 00:55:06.625
Have you seen Leonardo's
designs of weapons?

00:55:06.958 --> 00:55:11.250
Those designs can annihilate millions
of people in seconds.

00:55:11.833 --> 00:55:13.833
Isn't that art?

00:55:14.542 --> 00:55:16.125
Isn't that science?

00:55:17.250 --> 00:55:21.083
At least, the work you're doing
is helping a lot of people.

00:55:22.292 --> 00:55:24.875
It's hurting a few.

00:55:53.625 --> 00:56:01.250
Darling, what's wrong?

00:56:05.917 --> 00:56:09.041
What are you worried about?

00:56:09.042 --> 00:56:12.624
I think I'm trapped, Jaya.

00:56:12.625 --> 00:56:20.625
I don't know what I should do.
I've no idea.

00:56:22.708 --> 00:56:24.708
What happened?

00:56:27.375 --> 00:56:28.917
Tell me.

00:56:33.000 --> 00:56:40.457
I know that as a person you'll do the
right thing even if it's difficult.

00:56:40.458 --> 00:56:43.292
And as an artiste?

00:56:44.083 --> 00:56:52.083
- I don't get it. How is it different?
- It is different. Completely different.

00:56:57.500 --> 00:57:04.999
The rules of morality are not applicable
on artistes.

00:57:05.000 --> 00:57:09.666
Some famous artistes, writers, singers...

00:57:09.667 --> 00:57:13.666
Whatever their personal life might be...

00:57:13.667 --> 00:57:15.457
that's not people's concern.

00:57:15.458 --> 00:57:17.749
Ultimately, it's their work
that people remember.

00:57:17.750 --> 00:57:20.166
That's what remains, Jaya.
Isn't it?

00:57:20.167 --> 00:57:22.291
Which singer is a wife-beater?

00:57:22.292 --> 00:57:24.832
Which bloody cricketer has taken bribes?

00:57:24.833 --> 00:57:26.749
Which actor is a womaniser?

00:57:26.750 --> 00:57:29.207
No one remembers.

00:57:29.208 --> 00:57:33.832
No one wants to remember.

00:57:33.833 --> 00:57:36.041
What's the point?

00:57:36.042 --> 00:57:39.499
What are you talking about?

00:57:39.500 --> 00:57:41.499
I can't understand anything.

00:57:41.500 --> 00:57:47.332
Before this, no one else
had given me such a huge opportunity.

00:57:47.333 --> 00:57:48.791
You know.

00:57:48.792 --> 00:57:53.541
It's not just the money
but the work is challenging.

00:57:53.542 --> 00:57:59.041
He's challenged the artiste within me.
No one has done that before.

00:57:59.042 --> 00:58:02.249
This man gave me the opportunity
that the entire film industry couldn't.

00:58:02.250 --> 00:58:08.333
My makeup, my prosthetics, Jaya...

00:58:08.625 --> 00:58:11.333
How can I let that go?

00:58:13.250 --> 00:58:18.624
He didn't do it on purpose.

00:58:18.625 --> 00:58:22.875
Actually, he was in such a rush...

00:58:23.125 --> 00:58:27.874
Even we make mistakes in a hurry.

00:58:27.875 --> 00:58:33.417
Maybe, he pulled the trigger by mistake.

00:58:34.042 --> 00:58:36.500
And the man just got in the way.

00:58:37.542 --> 00:58:45.542
Yeah, got it?
He didn't do it on purpose.

00:59:05.958 --> 00:59:13.958
I'll be with you,
no matter what you do.

00:59:30.542 --> 00:59:38.542
I'm very worried about something.

00:59:39.708 --> 00:59:42.124
What do you have to worry about?

00:59:42.125 --> 00:59:50.125
- If one of the parents...
- Stammer.

00:59:52.208 --> 00:59:57.375
- Will the child...
- Stammer too?

01:00:01.750 --> 01:00:03.458
What?

01:00:06.208 --> 01:00:14.208
- I... Love... You...
- I love...

01:00:20.667 --> 01:00:24.208
Me too.

