<i>Tell me what should I do</i>

01:01:05.375 --> 01:01:12.832
<i>Hug my craziness
Adorn the tramlines with poetry</i>

01:01:12.833 --> 01:01:20.833
<i>My blunt sword lies in the pocket
Or empty it out at the next sale</i>

01:01:22.458 --> 01:01:29.582
<i>Every time I am in your neighbourhood</i>

01:01:29.583 --> 01:01:36.208
<i>I gulp my discomfort down my throat</i>

01:01:37.417 --> 01:01:44.625
<i>As I walk down the steps of your dreams</i>

01:01:44.958 --> 01:01:51.042
<i>That short, stout man stands in my way</i>

01:01:52.167 --> 01:01:56.917
<i>You are chasing a dream.
There's no one like that.</i>

01:01:57.583 --> 01:01:59.083
<i>You've met all the girls.</i>

01:02:00.583 --> 01:02:02.500
<i>I'm the only one left.</i>

01:02:03.292 --> 01:02:04.917
<i>You can look me up too.</i>

01:02:07.125 --> 01:02:08.417
<i>It's not a dream, it's reality.</i>

01:02:41.958 --> 01:02:49.458
<i>Candle lit dinners celebrating power cuts</i>

01:02:49.583 --> 01:02:54.875
<i>Tell me should I come back for more</i>

01:02:57.125 --> 01:03:04.582
<i>The food is burning on the stove
Our drinks are fizzling out</i>

