<i>The gas balloons have floated away
The blue salons look away</i>

01:04:08.083 --> 01:04:16.083
<i>Tell me where should I go</i>

01:04:20.667 --> 01:04:23.624
- Where's your driver, bro?
- I didn't call him.

01:04:23.625 --> 01:04:25.167
Hey, wait, wait, wait...

01:04:25.208 --> 01:04:28.416
You said you're calling your driver.
Why did you cancel?

01:04:28.417 --> 01:04:31.000
- Please don't drive.
- Nothing is going to happen to me.

01:04:32.292 --> 01:04:35.792
I can drive with one hand...

01:04:35.958 --> 01:04:37.999
In fact, I drive better when I'm drunk.

01:04:38.000 --> 01:04:40.500
- Bro, it's already happened once...
- Get out of my way.

01:04:40.667 --> 01:04:44.500
Why are you looking for trouble, bro?

01:04:44.667 --> 01:04:45.750
What did you just say?

01:04:46.375 --> 01:04:49.207
Nothing... Why don't you give me the keys?

01:04:49.208 --> 01:04:50.875
I'll drop you home.

01:04:51.167 --> 01:04:53.042
Why are you doing this?

01:04:53.458 --> 01:04:57.417
Have you forgotten my name and my surname?

01:04:58.417 --> 01:05:00.250
Nothing ever happens to me.

01:05:00.375 --> 01:05:01.708
What does that mean?

01:05:01.792 --> 01:05:03.458
Nothing can happen to me.

01:05:03.750 --> 01:05:05.916
Bro, I have the best intentions in mind.

01:05:05.917 --> 01:05:08.916
Those girls are waiting for you.
Go ahead.

01:05:08.917 --> 01:05:12.583
Drive carefully, bro.

01:05:12.875 --> 01:05:15.375
- I'll drop you.
- Just shut up.

01:05:16.875 --> 01:05:18.000
Bro...

01:05:18.833 --> 01:05:20.833
Bro, be careful...

01:05:28.667 --> 01:05:29.792
What the...

01:06:08.833 --> 01:06:11.292
Hello, sir!
Sir?

01:06:13.167 --> 01:06:14.917
- Sir?
- Yeah.

01:06:15.167 --> 01:06:16.500
Do you need some help?

01:06:17.708 --> 01:06:20.083
Yeah... Please come here.

01:06:20.625 --> 01:06:21.833
Please, please...

01:06:22.333 --> 01:06:25.916
Thank you...
Bloody irresponsible people...

01:06:25.917 --> 01:06:28.042
- Wonder who does these...
- Very irresponsible...

01:06:51.917 --> 01:06:53.833
The party is not over yet.

01:06:54.708 --> 01:06:58.042
The party has just started...

01:07:06.583 --> 01:07:11.667
<i>It's the time to disco...</i>

01:09:23.000 --> 01:09:24.208
Were you sleeping?

01:09:33.542 --> 01:09:34.542
How did it go?

01:09:34.750 --> 01:09:36.542
<i>It went according to the plan.</i>

01:09:36.750 --> 01:09:39.167
<i>It was a good thing
you did the makeup on hands.</i>

01:09:39.250 --> 01:09:41.333
<i>He was wearing a half sleeves shirt.</i>

01:09:42.958 --> 01:09:45.125
<i>This prosthetic thing...</i>

01:09:45.333 --> 01:09:47.417
<i>Even I don't know what happens to me.</i>

01:09:47.500 --> 01:09:49.625
<i>I become a different person.</i>

01:09:49.667 --> 01:09:51.833
<i>Your work is something else!</i>

01:09:52.542 --> 01:09:54.625
<i>Everything else was fine.</i>

01:09:55.333 --> 01:09:57.000
Absolutely perfect.

01:09:57.125 --> 01:09:59.542
It's a such huge job,
there will be some hiccups.

01:09:59.625 --> 01:10:02.707
There could have been a big accident while
I was trying to drive into the divider.

01:10:02.708 --> 01:10:04.125
I could have died.

01:10:04.333 --> 01:10:05.875
I just drove over...

01:10:06.958 --> 01:10:07.917
<i>He is a big guy.</i>

01:10:07.918 --> 01:10:11.625
I hurt my back, lifting him up.

01:10:11.708 --> 01:10:12.958
But that's okay.

01:10:13.125 --> 01:10:15.042
I had to block the road with bricks.

01:10:15.333 --> 01:10:16.750
It was a lot of hard work.

01:10:16.792 --> 01:10:20.457
The weight made it difficult.
I have a bad back.

01:10:20.458 --> 01:10:22.082
Otherwise, everything else was fine.

01:10:22.083 --> 01:10:24.084
Wiping off the finger print
is a very tedious task.

01:10:24.833 --> 01:10:26.458
<i>I did that properly.</i>

01:10:26.667 --> 01:10:32.542
<i>The handles, the seats,
the steering wheel, the entire car...</i>

01:10:33.000 --> 01:10:35.000
<i>I wiped everything down carefully.</i>

01:10:35.708 --> 01:10:38.333
<i>No one wears gloves while driving.</i>

01:10:39.083 --> 01:10:41.958
<i>And the gloves will be
visible on the CCTV too.</i>

01:10:42.250 --> 01:10:43.833
<i>It would have been a disaster.</i>

01:10:44.083 --> 01:10:45.958
<i>A complete disaster.</i>

01:10:51.583 --> 01:10:53.542
Here's your advance for the next job.

01:10:53.583 --> 01:10:54.917
Buy the materials you need.

01:10:55.000 --> 01:10:57.458
I'll brief you in some
time about the next job.

01:10:57.542 --> 01:11:00.375
Hope the net wasn't visible.

01:11:00.542 --> 01:11:02.541
After all you've been through...

01:11:02.542 --> 01:11:04.541
Hopefully, the blending didn't come off.

01:11:04.542 --> 01:11:05.999
I used very good adhesive.

01:11:06.000 --> 01:11:07.208
That I don't know.

01:11:07.583 --> 01:11:10.750
We'll get to know when the police watch
the CCTV footage on the big screen.

01:11:11.250 --> 01:11:14.292
I just concentrated on the acting.

01:11:16.792 --> 01:11:20.167
Hope no one was harmed this time.

01:11:20.333 --> 01:11:24.292
Only one person was harmed.

01:11:29.250 --> 01:11:31.874
- Manas...
- Who's asking?

01:11:31.875 --> 01:11:33.375
- Manas.
- Yeah.

01:11:35.542 --> 01:11:37.957
You have to wake up now, Manas.

01:11:37.958 --> 01:11:39.417
Who are you?

01:11:41.167 --> 01:11:44.542
I'm Poddar.

01:11:45.083 --> 01:11:46.542
DCDD Poddar.

01:11:48.750 --> 01:11:52.125
Sorry... Sorry, Inspector.

01:11:58.625 --> 01:11:59.833
Why am I here?

01:12:00.583 --> 01:12:02.042
How did I get here?

01:12:04.667 --> 01:12:09.166
You have run over five people while
driving under the influence of alcohol.

01:12:09.167 --> 01:12:11.625
Then you passed out
after hitting a divider.

01:12:11.792 --> 01:12:15.125
Then some responsible citizens
dropped you off here.

01:12:15.250 --> 01:12:17.250
Actually, they didn't want to.

01:12:17.417 --> 01:12:19.292
They wanted to lynch you to death.

01:12:19.333 --> 01:12:21.458
My men rescued you.

01:12:21.625 --> 01:12:23.374
What the hell are you saying?

01:12:23.375 --> 01:12:27.000
I couldn't have driven the car.
I was unconscious.

01:12:27.125 --> 01:12:33.208
A man... put a cloth on my mouth...

01:12:37.000 --> 01:12:40.542
Believe me, I had to get off the car once.

01:12:42.750 --> 01:12:46.625
How do you surround yourself
with criminals all the time?

01:12:48.167 --> 01:12:52.958
Last time, apparently your driver
ran over those people.

01:12:54.042 --> 01:12:58.542
This time some stranger had put you out...
You're really something!

01:12:59.708 --> 01:13:01.583
You don't believe me.

01:13:05.250 --> 01:13:07.750
I need a lawyer
and I need him right now.

01:13:07.833 --> 01:13:09.332
Of course.

01:13:09.333 --> 01:13:11.124
We will call the lawyer
once you're conscious.

01:13:11.125 --> 01:13:12.874
But I'm already in my senses.

01:13:12.875 --> 01:13:15.333
You're conscious now
but won't be 15 minutes later.

01:13:15.958 --> 01:13:17.625
Absolutely perfect.

01:13:18.250 --> 01:13:20.916
The way you got away with it last time...

01:13:20.917 --> 01:13:25.125
there's no guarantee that you won't get
away again, thanks to money and power.

01:13:25.333 --> 01:13:27.833
But this time the evidence against you
is strong.

01:13:28.125 --> 01:13:30.375
There was a camera at the traffic signal.

01:13:30.750 --> 01:13:31.750
Camera?

01:13:32.000 --> 01:13:33.000
Yes.

01:13:34.458 --> 01:13:40.250
It might take time in court
to prove that the footage is not fake.

01:13:40.708 --> 01:13:43.167
That's why we're taking care of you now.

01:13:43.750 --> 01:13:45.542
You can't do this.

01:13:46.375 --> 01:13:47.583
You cannot...

01:13:48.083 --> 01:13:49.083
Hey!

01:13:49.208 --> 01:13:51.625
Sit down!

01:13:54.625 --> 01:13:56.583
You are...

01:14:01.875 --> 01:14:04.125
Have you read Aesop's Fables?

01:14:05.042 --> 01:14:07.208
Or have you only watched porn?

01:14:07.792 --> 01:14:11.375
Remember the boy who cried wolf?

01:14:11.792 --> 01:14:15.292
The shepherd...
who bluffed over and over again.

01:14:16.500 --> 01:14:17.708
Remember the end?

01:14:22.125 --> 01:14:24.041
<i>This is the scene of a gruesome accident.</i>

01:14:24.042 --> 01:14:27.332
<i>Five people sleeping on the pavement
have been run over.</i>

01:14:27.333 --> 01:14:29.249
<i>Police have cordorned off this area.</i>

01:14:29.250 --> 01:14:31.416
<i>The bodies have been removed.</i>

01:14:31.417 --> 01:14:33.541
<i>An in depth investigation
is going on.</i>

01:14:33.542 --> 01:14:38.416
<i>The CCTV footage from the traffic camera
is also being looked at.</i>

01:14:38.417 --> 01:14:42.499
<i>This is the CCTV footage
where Manas Saha can be clearly seen.</i>

01:14:42.500 --> 01:14:46.875
<i>Common people have taken to the streets
in protest against this heinous incident.</i>

01:14:46.958 --> 01:14:48.499
<i>He can't do whatever he wants
just because he's a politician's son.</i>

01:14:48.500 --> 01:14:49.500
<i>We demand justice!</i>

01:14:49.501 --> 01:14:51.166
<i>This man should rot in jail.</i>

01:14:51.167 --> 01:14:53.749
<i>He got away with it last time.</i>

01:14:53.750 --> 01:14:55.249
<i>He should be punished.</i>

01:14:55.250 --> 01:14:57.917
<i>Down with Manas Saha!
We want justice!</i>

01:14:58.125 --> 01:15:00.916
<i>MLA Mrinmoy Saha insists
his son is innocent.</i>

01:15:00.917 --> 01:15:02.542
<i>Here's what he had to say.</i>

01:15:02.875 --> 01:15:05.416
<i>- Your son has been accused before?
- He was proven innocent.</i>

01:15:05.417 --> 01:15:06.582
<i>He'll be proved innocent again.</i>

01:15:06.583 --> 01:15:09.166
<i>We have CCTV footage
that shows he is guilty.</i>

01:15:09.167 --> 01:15:10.000
<i>It's fake.</i>

01:15:10.001 --> 01:15:14.457
<i>Even though, MLA Saha disagrees,
his son can be seen on the CCTV footage.</i>

01:15:14.458 --> 01:15:18.750
<i>Manas Saha got away last time
for the lack of evidence.</i>

01:15:19.208 --> 01:15:21.333
<i>We have very strong evidence this time.</i>

01:15:21.458 --> 01:15:23.625
<i>That's why it'll be difficult for him.</i>

01:15:23.833 --> 01:15:25.124
<i>Easily IPC Section...</i>

01:15:25.125 --> 01:15:25.917
304A...

01:15:25.917 --> 01:15:26.833
<i>304A...</i>

01:15:26.833 --> 01:15:27.750
279...

01:15:27.750 --> 01:15:28.708
<i>279...</i>

01:15:28.708 --> 01:15:29.417
337...

