338...

01:15:30.792 --> 01:15:31.792
<i>338...</i>

01:15:31.793 --> 01:15:37.208
<i>427 and read with 181, 185
of motor vehicles act of 1980...</i>

01:15:37.542 --> 01:15:40.375
<i>We're charging him
under all these sections.</i>

01:15:41.000 --> 01:15:42.500
Good.

01:15:48.042 --> 01:15:53.458
<i>Manas Saha is involved in a hit and
run case that killed five people.</i>

01:15:54.458 --> 01:15:58.708
<i>He even tried to destroy
the traffic camera.</i>

01:15:58.958 --> 01:16:03.833
<i>Common people are protesting
the deaths of the poor people.</i>

01:16:04.208 --> 01:16:06.457
<i>The police have blocked the area.</i>

01:16:06.458 --> 01:16:11.957
<i>The cyber forensic team is verifying
the authenticity of the CCTV footage.</i>

01:16:11.958 --> 01:16:16.333
<i>This is the second time Manas Saha
is involved in a hit and run case.</i>

01:16:17.917 --> 01:16:20.958
<i>Manas Saha has been arrested.</i>

01:16:21.042 --> 01:16:23.832
<i>He's being held for questioning
for the last 24 hours.</i>

01:16:23.833 --> 01:16:28.625
<i>DCDD Poddar was unavailable
for comments.</i>

01:17:00.083 --> 01:17:04.208
Sir, please buy some incense sticks.

01:17:04.750 --> 01:17:06.833
Please, sir.

01:17:07.042 --> 01:17:08.416
I don't want.

01:17:08.417 --> 01:17:11.708
This is not a market.
This is an accident site.

01:17:11.833 --> 01:17:14.250
It's very cheap.
Please buy one.

01:17:16.458 --> 01:17:19.292
- How much is it for?
- Rs. 10.

01:17:30.000 --> 01:17:31.125
Take it.

01:17:42.292 --> 01:17:44.708
I bought your incense stick.
Why are you crying?

01:17:48.208 --> 01:17:52.999
Someone drove a car over my father.

01:17:53.000 --> 01:17:57.417
It was really hot.
So, he had come to sleep here.

01:18:04.625 --> 01:18:07.250
Hey, wait.

01:18:13.833 --> 01:18:15.208
Keep this.

01:18:16.667 --> 01:18:19.333
Take this money.

01:18:20.167 --> 01:18:23.250
- Please take it.
- I don't want it. I don't need it.

01:18:24.708 --> 01:18:25.708
Where do you live?

01:18:34.667 --> 01:18:39.083
Mom, this gentleman wanted to meet you.

01:18:43.792 --> 01:18:45.167
I...

01:18:46.917 --> 01:18:49.917
Wanted to give him...

01:18:50.292 --> 01:18:52.250
some money...

01:18:54.042 --> 01:18:57.167
But he didn't want to take it.

01:18:58.792 --> 01:19:03.541
I wanted to give it to you...

01:19:03.542 --> 01:19:04.667
Why?

01:19:04.792 --> 01:19:11.666
Because of the accident...

01:19:11.667 --> 01:19:14.500
I wanted to help...

01:19:15.083 --> 01:19:17.292
We don't need your money.

01:19:17.625 --> 01:19:19.875
Please take some incense sticks
if you want.

01:19:44.750 --> 01:19:46.708
You can't say no.

01:19:48.000 --> 01:19:49.583
This is the last one.

01:19:49.792 --> 01:19:51.500
We'll be done after that.

01:19:52.167 --> 01:19:55.833
You have to work really hard
on this Saturday's makeup.

01:19:56.500 --> 01:20:01.542
- No.
- Look at you being all pricey.

01:20:01.833 --> 01:20:04.000
I know you're a great artiste.

01:20:04.542 --> 01:20:06.208
What do you want?

01:20:06.333 --> 01:20:07.417
More money.

01:20:07.583 --> 01:20:12.167
I don't want any money.
I'm not an artiste. I want nothing!

01:20:13.917 --> 01:20:18.291
How strange! The great Vinci Da is saying
he's not an artiste.

01:20:18.292 --> 01:20:20.292
What's wrong with you?

01:20:22.208 --> 01:20:25.083
I can't kill any more.

01:20:27.250 --> 01:20:32.542
Why are you so stressed out?

01:20:32.875 --> 01:20:34.917
You're not the one kiling them.

01:20:35.250 --> 01:20:37.375
I'm killing them.

01:20:38.417 --> 01:20:42.333
Do you have a problem when an animal
is sacrificed at the altar of God?

01:20:45.167 --> 01:20:46.750
That's what this is.

01:20:47.125 --> 01:20:48.875
This is sacrifice.

01:20:49.125 --> 01:20:53.625
How will we pacify the God of Law
without sacrifice?

01:20:58.625 --> 01:21:00.750
You are crazy.

01:21:01.542 --> 01:21:02.542
You are sick.

01:21:02.543 --> 01:21:04.750
You are mad!

01:21:05.875 --> 01:21:09.832
Yes but there's a method
to the madness.

01:21:09.833 --> 01:21:12.916
If you continue your drama...

01:21:12.917 --> 01:21:17.208
I'll tell the cops that you're the
mastermind behind these crimes.

01:21:17.917 --> 01:21:19.832
It's a high profile case.

01:21:19.833 --> 01:21:23.250
My victims will be more than happy
to get a witness.

01:21:23.583 --> 01:21:27.416
There are no videos of me wearing
or taking off the masks.

01:21:27.417 --> 01:21:31.583
<i>But you're in videos making Shyamsundar
and Manas' masks.</i>

01:21:31.625 --> 01:21:34.500
I have lots of videos.

01:21:40.833 --> 01:21:44.791
What's my fault?
Please let me go.

01:21:44.792 --> 01:21:46.666
Please let me go.

01:21:46.667 --> 01:21:52.542
I haven't harmed you.
Why are you doing this to me?

01:21:54.625 --> 01:21:56.833
This is the last case.

01:21:57.625 --> 01:21:59.458
That's it.

01:22:00.750 --> 01:22:05.208
Time for "The Last Supper".

01:22:09.917 --> 01:22:13.792
Please don't betray me
at the last moment like Judas.

01:22:14.042 --> 01:22:15.792
Please...

01:22:16.042 --> 01:22:19.083
After the job is done
I'll give you the videos.

01:22:19.375 --> 01:22:22.333
You can watch it on your day off.

01:22:27.625 --> 01:22:28.917
Reference.

01:22:28.958 --> 01:22:32.458
<i>Sunny Sen, page three
celebrity, known rapist.</i>

01:22:39.917 --> 01:22:44.624
<i>Have you ever seen the eyes
of a listless, trapped mouse?</i>

01:22:44.625 --> 01:22:52.625
<i>It knows the moment the mouse trap
is opened like a reverse guillotine...</i>

01:22:53.458 --> 01:23:00.750
<i>Hundreds of crows will swoop in and relish
it's entrails like cheap roadside snack.</i>

01:23:01.583 --> 01:23:03.833
<i>That's how I felt.</i>

01:23:04.208 --> 01:23:06.542
<i>There was nowhere to run.</i>

01:23:06.792 --> 01:23:11.375
<i>Either the cops will get me
or the crazy Adi Bose will kill me.</i>

01:23:11.833 --> 01:23:17.750
<i>Or I'll kill myself, guilty of having
innocent blood on my hands.</i>

01:23:18.083 --> 01:23:19.792
<i>But still...</i>

01:23:20.250 --> 01:23:23.792
<i>Even though I'm telling the story
in this deep, sombre voice...</i>

01:23:24.083 --> 01:23:27.542
<i>the story was being
written by someone else.</i>

01:23:28.083 --> 01:23:29.958
<i>The one who writes all the stories.</i>

01:23:30.417 --> 01:23:32.833
<i>The person sitting up above.</i>

01:24:35.125 --> 01:24:36.249
Who are you?

01:24:36.250 --> 01:24:39.125
Go away... Go away!

01:24:39.458 --> 01:24:41.457
Leave me alone...
I haven't done anything.

01:24:41.458 --> 01:24:43.999
Get out of here.

01:24:44.000 --> 01:24:45.791
I haven't killed anyone.
Why is there so much blood?

01:24:45.792 --> 01:24:49.917
Go away...
Get out!!!

01:24:50.125 --> 01:24:52.250
I haven't killed anyone.

01:25:17.750 --> 01:25:19.333
<i>How long has it been circulating?</i>

01:25:19.625 --> 01:25:20.957
Since yesterday.

01:25:20.958 --> 01:25:22.582
Have you searched Sunny Sen's home?

01:25:22.583 --> 01:25:23.750
Yes, sir.

01:25:23.875 --> 01:25:25.875
We've found a lot of discriminating videos.

01:25:26.083 --> 01:25:30.291
He has filmed himself too.

01:25:30.292 --> 01:25:32.707
The man is mentally disturbed.
He's psychotic.

01:25:32.708 --> 01:25:34.417
He's disgusting.

01:25:35.333 --> 01:25:37.792
Bring it to me on a pen drive.

01:25:40.500 --> 01:25:41.917
Go on.

01:25:42.583 --> 01:25:46.000
Sir... I have it.

01:25:46.375 --> 01:25:50.000
Someone forwarded it.
Would you like to take a look?

01:26:05.375 --> 01:26:06.875
Who sent it to you?

01:26:08.250 --> 01:26:14.375
One of my college friends...

01:26:19.875 --> 01:26:21.792
Ask the bugger to come here.

01:26:22.917 --> 01:26:25.542
Let me introduce him to the Cyber cell.

01:26:26.667 --> 01:26:30.208
And please don't call disgusting people
like these your friends.

01:26:31.125 --> 01:26:34.458
Otherwise, you'll be in trouble too.
Understood?

01:26:35.417 --> 01:26:36.791
Understood?

01:26:36.792 --> 01:26:40.250
- Yes, sir.
- Get out. Get out!

01:26:44.708 --> 01:26:46.416
And delete that video!

01:26:46.417 --> 01:26:49.957
<i>I heard Sunny Sen got very badly beaten up
in the lock up.</i>

01:26:49.958 --> 01:26:55.167
<i>Apparently, some of his nerves
were permanently damaged.</i>

01:26:56.000 --> 01:26:59.417
<i>But he got out on bail.
Thanks to his contacts.</i>

01:26:59.750 --> 01:27:04.000
<i>Although, by then his personal life
was already falling apart.</i>

01:27:04.208 --> 01:27:07.333
<i>Sunny's father-in-law
was a very influential man.</i>

01:27:07.375 --> 01:27:13.458
<i>Sunny's wife filed for divorce
and took full custody of his children.</i>

01:27:14.292 --> 01:27:16.417
<i>This case was pending already.</i>

01:27:16.792 --> 01:27:21.249
<i>Although, his lawyer tried to prove
that the videos were fake...</i>

01:27:21.250 --> 01:27:23.166
<i>forensics found no proof
in support of the claim.</i>

01:27:23.167 --> 01:27:27.375
<i>Adi Bose destroyed Sunny Sen's life.</i>

01:27:27.917 --> 01:27:33.417
<i>Unknowingly, he had destroyed another life.</i>

01:27:34.500 --> 01:27:35.917
<i>Mine.</i>

01:27:38.333 --> 01:27:42.917
I'm so happy that you've finally come home.

01:27:45.125 --> 01:27:48.208
You don't look like someone
who parties a lot.

01:27:48.833 --> 01:27:52.083
An occasional drink for the artiste.
That's it.

01:27:53.292 --> 01:27:56.582
I don't go out much.

01:27:56.583 --> 01:27:58.167
Work keeps me busy.

01:27:58.250 --> 01:28:00.667
But it's a special occasion.

01:28:00.917 --> 01:28:03.083
- And your list...
- No formalities, please...

01:28:03.625 --> 01:28:07.333
Right... Your list is done.

01:28:07.958 --> 01:28:09.750
And I'm done too.

01:28:09.958 --> 01:28:13.083
It's over...
All the work.

01:28:13.250 --> 01:28:16.500
So, I was saying...

01:28:16.708 --> 01:28:18.958
- So?
- That...

01:28:19.417 --> 01:28:23.417
If I can get the videos and photos...

01:28:24.292 --> 01:28:26.375
I mean...

01:28:27.625 --> 01:28:31.208
You know I thought about it a lot.

01:28:32.833 --> 01:28:34.250
It's safe with me.

01:28:37.417 --> 01:28:41.833
I'll keep it like a memento.

01:28:46.875 --> 01:28:50.125
Only the prosthetic list is over.

01:28:50.375 --> 01:28:53.000
But the list of criminals is long.

01:28:53.292 --> 01:28:54.916
There's so much more to do.

01:28:54.917 --> 01:28:57.249
You're done but I'm not.

01:28:57.250 --> 01:28:59.417
There's so much more to do.

01:29:00.375 --> 01:29:02.792
The laws...

01:29:04.542 --> 01:29:09.125
So many people are breaking the law
and getting away with it.

01:29:09.458 --> 01:29:11.957
Let's say you suddenly get mad at me.

01:29:11.958 --> 01:29:14.708
And you take a trip to the police station.

01:29:16.875 --> 01:29:21.708
And one story might lead to another...

01:29:23.875 --> 01:29:27.500
Then, my "Clean Society Mission"
will be in danger.

01:29:27.750 --> 01:29:29.083
So, let it be with me.

01:29:31.292 --> 01:29:32.500
What's this?

01:29:38.292 --> 01:29:40.083
Like you said...

01:29:40.375 --> 01:29:41.750
Memento.

01:29:44.250 --> 01:29:49.458
I bought it from a little boy
on the streets.

01:29:50.250 --> 01:29:52.166
You burn incense while drinking?

01:29:52.167 --> 01:29:55.542
Is that some strange artiste's ritual?

01:30:01.417 --> 01:30:06.375
That girl who...

01:30:06.500 --> 01:30:08.041
Did you know her?

01:30:08.042 --> 01:30:11.375
No, random.
I picked up the first girl I saw.

01:30:12.458 --> 01:30:14.917
Not someone I knew.

01:30:21.667 --> 01:30:23.375
Collateral damage...
I told you.

01:30:23.417 --> 01:30:27.167
- Collateral...
- Yeah, collateral damage.

01:30:27.333 --> 01:30:32.125
What about Sunny Sen's lawyer?

01:30:32.208 --> 01:30:37.374
What if he orders for medical tests?

01:30:37.375 --> 01:30:40.500
The marks are still there.

01:30:40.708 --> 01:30:44.707
He can prove that it wasn't Sunny Sen.

01:30:44.708 --> 01:30:45.500
What happens then?

01:30:45.501 --> 01:30:48.667
There'll be a lot of trouble.

01:30:51.375 --> 01:30:55.500
I use gloves when I murder someone.

01:30:56.417 --> 01:30:59.249
I used a condom when I raped the girl.

01:30:59.250 --> 01:31:00.958
Condom?

01:31:05.167 --> 01:31:06.167
<i>What's wrong with you?</i>

01:31:06.583 --> 01:31:07.917
Are you okay?

01:31:09.083 --> 01:31:10.375
Okay?

01:31:12.292 --> 01:31:16.666
My drink is a little too stiff.
Can I get some water?

01:31:16.667 --> 01:31:19.750
- Water?
- It's over.

01:31:20.458 --> 01:31:21.917
I'll get it right away.

01:31:33.083 --> 01:31:35.542
Why did you ask me to meet here?

01:31:36.708 --> 01:31:38.625
What are you doing?

01:31:41.458 --> 01:31:42.750
What's that?

01:31:43.875 --> 01:31:46.917
Have you lost your mind?

01:31:47.417 --> 01:31:51.125
What do you want me to see?

01:31:51.458 --> 01:31:53.000
What do you have on your mobile...

01:32:16.833 --> 01:32:19.750
This is an accident.

01:32:20.125 --> 01:32:23.541
How is it your fault?

01:32:23.542 --> 01:32:26.750
Accidents happen.

01:32:30.167 --> 01:32:33.749
Jaya, this is not your fault.

01:32:33.750 --> 01:32:37.000
This video is an accident, Jaya.

01:32:37.542 --> 01:32:41.041
This is an accident!

01:32:41.042 --> 01:32:48.583
Then why are people blaming me?
Everyone...

01:32:50.708 --> 01:32:52.416
What am I going to do now?

01:32:52.417 --> 01:32:53.817
Why are you giving them importance?

01:32:54.000 --> 01:32:59.500
You don't have to pay attention
to what people say.

01:33:00.167 --> 01:33:03.374
They're idiots
if they think it's your fault.

01:33:03.375 --> 01:33:08.417
If anyone looks at you,
I'll blind them.

01:33:08.583 --> 01:33:10.374
Please calm down.

01:33:10.375 --> 01:33:13.833
Where are you going?

01:33:14.417 --> 01:33:15.707
I'm asking you to stop.

01:33:15.708 --> 01:33:18.667
Stop! What are you doing?

01:33:19.250 --> 01:33:22.249
Have you gone mad?
What are you doing?

01:33:22.250 --> 01:33:23.833
What was in your hand?

01:33:24.458 --> 01:33:26.417
Jaya!

01:33:27.542 --> 01:33:32.375
I don't want to live anymore.

01:33:32.875 --> 01:33:35.957
I want to die...

01:33:35.958 --> 01:33:39.708
Have you gone mad?
Why do you want to die?

01:33:40.167 --> 01:33:43.042
People don't remember these things.
They forget.

01:33:43.750 --> 01:33:47.708
It's just going to be you and me.
Just us.

01:33:48.208 --> 01:33:53.500
We'll live with our heads held high, Jaya.

01:33:53.708 --> 01:33:58.874
I will always respect you.

01:33:58.875 --> 01:34:04.333
Your body has nothing
to do with your honour.

01:34:04.542 --> 01:34:08.125
We'll go somewhere far away.

01:34:09.292 --> 01:34:12.832
Why should you cry?
Why should you be ashamed?

01:34:12.833 --> 01:34:16.082
Why should you pay for the crime
you didn't commit?

01:34:16.083 --> 01:34:21.458
The criminal will be punished.

01:35:49.875 --> 01:35:52.542
Sir, this is an open and shut case.

01:35:52.750 --> 01:35:54.916
That's what the video evidence is saying.

01:35:54.917 --> 01:35:58.167
- He had a criminal record, right?
- Yes, sir.

01:35:59.375 --> 01:36:03.750
He was psychologically damaged.
Murdered his father as a boy.

01:36:04.125 --> 01:36:10.375
There are fingerprints on the glass.
His laptop is at the cyber forensic cell.

01:36:13.250 --> 01:36:18.167
- Everything is okay but...
- But what, sir?

01:36:19.250 --> 01:36:21.667
I've seen this man before.

01:36:22.333 --> 01:36:23.917
He looks familiar.

01:36:24.208 --> 01:36:25.791
- Where?
- At the police station.

01:36:25.792 --> 01:36:27.625
At the police station?

01:36:30.042 --> 01:36:34.416
Oh! I remember now!

01:36:34.417 --> 01:36:39.083
I met him at your station.

01:36:40.500 --> 01:36:42.666
- Bapi, you were there too.
- Yes, sir.

01:36:42.667 --> 01:36:48.125
That... Pickpocket...
Beaten up by the mob...

01:36:48.375 --> 01:36:49.167
Remember, Bapi?

01:36:49.168 --> 01:36:50.291
Yes, sir.

01:36:50.292 --> 01:36:51.958
Right, sir. He was there.

01:36:52.417 --> 01:36:58.875
He went on about Law
like a mad man.

01:36:59.417 --> 01:37:01.083
Mad man.

01:37:01.833 --> 01:37:04.375
But Law comes before everyone, sir.

01:37:04.500 --> 01:37:06.208
Life and death are secondary.

01:37:06.583 --> 01:37:10.250
The confession confirms the mental illness.

01:37:12.417 --> 01:37:14.750
Something isn't adding up.

01:37:16.208 --> 01:37:18.917
Something is out of place.

01:37:24.667 --> 01:37:26.124
What's wrong with you?

01:37:26.125 --> 01:37:27.583
Is everything okay?

01:37:28.583 --> 01:37:30.042
Okay?

01:37:32.000 --> 01:37:36.207
My drink is a little too stiff.
Can I get some water?

01:37:36.208 --> 01:37:39.125
- Water?
- Yeah, it's over.

01:37:39.833 --> 01:37:41.500
I'll get it right away.

01:38:16.875 --> 01:38:23.208
Vinci Da, don't know what I would do
without you.

01:38:24.083 --> 01:38:26.875
I wouldn't be able to become
a successful lawyer.

01:38:28.667 --> 01:38:32.707
- Lawyer?
- Yes, lawyer.

01:38:32.708 --> 01:38:34.500
What do lawyers do?

01:38:35.625 --> 01:38:40.875
Lawyers bring criminals to justice.

01:38:41.708 --> 01:38:43.625
That's what I do.

01:38:45.083 --> 01:38:48.833
My friends used to play cops and crooks.

01:38:49.250 --> 01:38:51.500
I went a step further.

01:38:52.042 --> 01:38:57.125
Crooks... Cops...
Lawyer.

01:38:58.708 --> 01:39:02.000
Needless to say,
I would play the lawyer.

01:39:02.833 --> 01:39:05.832
Everything must be taken to court.

01:39:05.833 --> 01:39:07.500
We used to play a game too.

01:39:07.708 --> 01:39:09.125
Crooks and cops?

01:39:11.208 --> 01:39:13.042
A little more than that.

01:39:14.833 --> 01:39:16.667
Crooks, cops and lawyer?

01:39:17.792 --> 01:39:22.125
Ubermenschen think alike.

01:39:22.333 --> 01:39:24.375
A little more.

01:39:29.667 --> 01:39:31.125
What's that?

01:39:32.292 --> 01:39:35.207
Crooks, cops, lawyer...

01:39:35.208 --> 01:39:38.000
Judge and Executioner.

01:39:41.917 --> 01:39:45.042
- Which character did you play?
- Double role.

01:39:45.750 --> 01:39:48.542
Judge and Executioner.

01:41:03.875 --> 01:41:05.833
I am Adi Bose.

01:41:07.833 --> 01:41:10.042
In sound mind...

01:41:10.792 --> 01:41:13.042
Without any provocation from anyone...

01:41:14.583 --> 01:41:16.917
is committing suicide.

01:41:20.083 --> 01:41:25.917
The only one responsible
for my death is me...

